{"tid":2167451,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黑熊抱行山女摸大脾慘遭絕育","createTime":"2020-08-21T06:18:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T07:14:25.000Z","uid":1886,"like":243,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"1e4852da5500d50f7b24ef336c46ed4ad16f9faf","tid":2167451,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:18:19.000Z","msg":"上月在墨西哥，一名女子到生態公園行山時險遭劫色。涉事的黑熊不但施展熊抱，還摸了女子的大腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，女子淡定舉機與黑熊自拍的影片在網絡瘋傳。不過這張爆紅的合照卻促使當局將黑熊移送至另一個山脈，以及為牠絕育<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，惹來當地部份居民不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200814/6BTNYNO7HJDODI4DFVRIZY4WKA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200814%2F6BTNYNO7HJDODI4DFVRIZY4WKA%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu3O0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=a2c1aa21\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200814%2F6BTNYNO7HJDODI4DFVRIZY4WKA%2F&h=5ee8db4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200814/6BTNYNO7HJDODI4DFVRIZY4WKA/</a>"},{"pid":"1d7d24a7498ee7e921f2b4fb421cfe2d77208f3b","tid":2167451,"uid":1886,"like":77,"dislike":1,"score":76,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:18:53.000Z","msg":"事發於上月，幾名女子在奇平科生態公園（Chipinque Ecological Park）行山時，偶遇一隻黑熊，眾人即時一動不動，不敢驚動牠。不過黑熊似乎「色迷心竅」，走到其中一人身旁站起，湊近去嗅女子的秀髮，更伸手欲熊抱她。而女子則表現得很淡定，拿出手機拍下這個尷尬的場面。黑熊之後離開，沒有傷害眾人。黑熊「性騷擾」女子的過程被途人拍低，影片迅速在互聯網瘋傳。"},{"pid":"040a686f22d4143b4c88bfe4631ee080d04228ce","tid":2167451,"uid":1886,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:19:44.000Z","msg":"雖然黑熊未有對途人造成傷害，但仍難逃被清算命運。墨西哥當局憂慮黑熊會對生態公園的遊客構成風險，決定為牠絕育。專家指出，在公園生活的黑熊群已習慣被遊客餵食，擔憂有遊客會仿效片中女子，以食物利誘黑熊自拍，或觸動黑熊作出一些不能預料的反應。有研究黑熊的科學家表示，雖然黑熊甚少襲擊遊人，惟北美每年平均亦有1人遇襲死亡。當地官員就稱，園裏的黑熊已屢次接觸遊人，事件中的黑熊Chipi更曾被發現在民居附近出沒，所以有必要進行絕育。"},{"pid":"ca3f721375178c5804bd931cd6d8772cc3eb88bc","tid":2167451,"uid":147629,"like":266,"dislike":3,"score":263,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:21:04.000Z","msg":"惟北美每年平均亦有1人遇襲死亡，一人會唔會太少，咁應該安全過貓狗幾十到幾百倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ebc2f1655119e1eca227b1df471fb200cb03fb2","tid":2167451,"uid":156542,"like":133,"dislike":2,"score":131,"quote":{"pid":"ca3f721375178c5804bd931cd6d8772cc3eb88bc","tid":2167451,"uid":147629,"like":266,"dislike":3,"score":263,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:21:04.000Z","msg":"惟北美每年平均亦有1人遇襲死亡，一人會唔會太少，咁應該安全過貓狗幾十到幾百倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:22:11.000Z","msg":"安全過蛇 蜘蛛嗰啲啦"},{"pid":"ea8a38ac9014b126c509fa6c4c97a12ef97db58b","tid":2167451,"uid":144626,"like":122,"dislike":2,"score":120,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:23:31.000Z","msg":"條女條係咪外賣妹<br />\n識無敵風火輪?"},{"pid":"b5e170d33909c35ad2ba285d7dd6f24fa0f323f5","tid":2167451,"uid":202011,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:23:35.000Z","msg":"頭先睇錯右邊幅圖 以為隻熊含住條女個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw熊仔好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8fef68934f9739bc1688886142f68b0b0b81fc5","tid":2167451,"uid":194399,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:25:20.000Z","msg":"隻黑熊睇黎幾溫馴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8670dfbd14c89024fcedacccca1f3c780bf13673","tid":2167451,"uid":273157,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:26:14.000Z","msg":"個女人似熊"},{"pid":"3b3f7f30c34ed64b761ef1d4f1f1a7c74470ef64","tid":2167451,"uid":331739,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:27:54.000Z","msg":"外賣仔等陣就去打鳩佢"},{"pid":"b55f35bc53dab15d2e1dc6a704b716d5575e4052","tid":2167451,"uid":271199,"like":76,"dislike":1,"score":75,"quote":{"pid":"ca3f721375178c5804bd931cd6d8772cc3eb88bc","tid":2167451,"uid":147629,"like":266,"dislike":3,"score":263,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:21